OL,5, Understaffing at HM Revenue & Customs  
OL,6, is causing unacceptable delays and     
OL,7, hindering economic activity, according 
OL,8, to a leading accountants' group.       
OL,10,FThe Institute of Chartered Accountants 
OL,11,Fof England and Wales (ICAEW) said      
OL,12,Fsecuring basic tax details takes months
OL,13,Fand is causing delays for companies.   
OL,15,FOne accountant called the service      
OL,16,F"diabolical" and the institute wants an
OL,17,Femergency taskforce drafted in.        
OL,19,FHMRC said it was responding to most    
OL,20,Fcorrespondence within 15 days.         
